<p>Aquí puedes verlo en acción:&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



<p>Similar a compañías como Apple, <strong>Casper ha transformado algo tan mundano como el desempacar su producto, en una experiencia memorable y que vale la pena compartir.</strong>&nbsp;</p>



<p>De hecho, van tan lejos como a alentarte a documentar tu experiencia desempacando el producto en la página de preguntas frecuentes (FAQ).</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="462" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-1024x462.png" alt="4 Casper_s FAQ Page" class="wp-image-113753" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-1024x462.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-300x135.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-768x347.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-380x171.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-600x271.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-760x343.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-1440x650.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-78x35.png 78w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-111x50.png 111w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-740x334.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-220x99.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page-385x174.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Casper_s-FAQ-Page.png 1485w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>El desempacar (mejor conocido como “unboxing”) es otra tendencia que Casper ha capitalizado, debido a su creciente interés en años recientes.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="442" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-1024x442.png" alt="5 Unboxing in Google Trends" class="wp-image-113757" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-1024x442.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-300x129.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-768x331.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-1536x662.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-380x164.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-600x259.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-760x328.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-1440x621.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-81x35.png 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-116x50.png 116w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-740x319.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-220x95.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Unboxing-in-Google-Trends-385x166.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-